	* lisp/GNUmakefile.in (uninstall): New target.
	* doc/GNUmakefile.in (ii-args): New var.
	(install): Use $(ii-args).
	(uninstall): New target.
	* GNUmakefile.in (uninstall): New target.

2008-07-12  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

