	Use `edb--meta1D' and `edb--1D!'.
	(db-write-1, db-write-intdelim): Use `edb--1D'.

	* db-interfa.el
	(db-kill-all-buffers, db-save-some-buffers, db-find-file):
	(db-find-read-in-database, db-revert-database, db-save-database):
