	(parse-time-string): Likewise.

	* edb.texi (Nonregular database example):
	Use `match-string' in example code.

2004-07-24  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@surf.glug.org>

	* db-util.el (db-vararg-call):
	No longer use `subseq'; do it "manually".

